// The Ledger, chapter 5 of 5: THE RAID. The reward finale - reached ONLY by
// the fight (SELL) path of chapter 4. When you break the Auditor gunship and
// take the payday, Vesh spends a slice of it hiring you the one thing the whole
// campaign never let you fly: a capital ship with torpedoes. You take her, with
// two of Vesh's wing on small escorts, and go settle the Magpie account -
// raiding their forward base among the rocks. This is the victory lap: go HAM.
//
// Reachability: ch4's Auditor-death (SELL, choice == 1) handler chains here with
// NextScenario. The BURN ending stays terminal (no fight, no chain). Variables
// do not survive scenario changes, so ch5 seeds its own from scratch.
//
// Cast:
//   - player_spaceship: a cargoB-class gunship (the Auditor's own hull-class),
//     Player-driven. Guns on LMB (the two turret cubes), torpedoes on a
//     dedicated RMB / left-trigger (the two torpedo bays). infinite_ammo so the
//     hero moment is not magazine-gated.
//   - wing_1 / wing_2: two AI escorts on the player's side (allegiance Player),
//     small racer hulls; they fly in and engage the defenders.
//   - raider_1..4: four AI Magpie fighters (default Enemy), small racers,
//     orbiting and leashed to the base so they defend it instead of scattering.
//   - magpie_base: a real multi-section station (Hull + Turret, a controller
//     core, NO thrusters so it holds station), Enemy. Destructible - cracking
//     it is part of the win, the torpedoes' target.
//
// Win: all four raiders down AND the base destroyed -> Victory (terminal - this
// is the campaign's end, no chain). Player death -> Defeat + retry ch5. Both
// outcome handlers gate act == 1 and latch a distinct terminal act (2 win, 3
// loss), so whichever lands first closes the act and the other cannot overwrite
// it (outcome-is-last-write-wins).
[
    Scenario((
        id: "ledger_ch5_the_raid",
        name: "The Ledger 5: The Raid",
        description: "Payday buys a gunship. Take the big ship and two of Vesh's wing and go settle the Magpie account - raid their forward base among the rocks. The reward finale of The Ledger.",
        cubemap: "dep://base/textures/cubemap.png",
        thumbnail: Some("dep://base/textures/asteroid.png"),
        // hidden: false (temporarily) so the finale can be launched directly
        // from the Scenarios picker for playtesting. RE-HIDE before release - it
        // is meant to be reached only by winning the ch4 fight.
        hidden: false,
        events: [
            (
                name: OnStart,
                filters: [],
                actions: [
                    // act: 1 = raiding, 2 = won, 3 = lost. Both terminals latch
                    // act so the loser cannot overwrite the winner.
                    VariableSet((
                        key: "act",
                        expression: Term(Factor(Literal(Number(1.0)))),
                    )),
                    // raiders_left counts the four defending fighters down; the
                    // base is tracked separately (base_down). Victory needs both.
                    VariableSet((
                        key: "raiders_left",
                        expression: Term(Factor(Literal(Number(4.0)))),
                    )),
                    VariableSet((
                        key: "base_down",
                        expression: Term(Factor(Literal(Number(0.0)))),
                    )),
                    // One-shot guards for the deferred Victory and the base line.
                    VariableSet((
                        key: "win_said",
                        expression: Term(Factor(Literal(Number(0.0)))),
                    )),
                    VariableSet((
                        key: "base_said",
                        expression: Term(Factor(Literal(Number(0.0)))),
                    )),
                    StoryMessage((
                        speaker: "Broker Vesh",
                        text: "Here is what your payday bought, Kestrel: a gunship with teeth, and two of my wing to fly cover. The Magpies have a forward post out in the rocks - the same crew that shadowed you in the channel. Go settle it. LMB is your guns, and the R key drops those torpedo tubes. Crack the base and clean up their fighters.",
                    )),
                    Objective((
                        id: "obj_raid",
                        message: "Ch.5 - The Raid: destroy the Magpie base and its four fighters.",
                    )),
                    // --- The gunship: the player's cargoB-class capital hull.
                    // Guns (the two turret cubes) on LMB; torpedoes (the two
                    // torpedo bays) on RMB / left-trigger - a real torpedo
                    // trigger, the one time the campaign hands the player one.
