                    // --- The Magpie base: a custom station built from a
                    // reinforced-hull keep around a controller core, with two
                    // turrets and two RCS thrusters. The thrusters give its
                    // controller the RCS authority to STATION-KEEP against the
                    // (mild, reduced) gravity here; a tight leash (15u, centred on
                    // its spawn) keeps it from chasing the player when it engages
                    // - beyond the leash the AILeash tether breaks off combat and
                    // pulls it home. Enemy, destructible - the torpedoes' target.
